---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/home.css';
---

<Layout title="PlayGames - Spartanburg's Premier Card & Game Shop">
	
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="hero">
		<h1>Welcome to PlayGames</h1>
		<p>Spartanburg's Premier Destination for Trading Cards & Gaming</p>
		<p class="location">📍 Located in Spartanburg, SC</p>
		<a href="/onlineShop" class="cta-button">Explore Our Collection</a>
	</section>

	<!-- Features Grid -->
	<section class="features">
		<div class="feature-card">
			<div class="feature-title-group">
				<div class="feature-icon">🎴</div>
				<h3>Premium Cards</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Discover an extensive collection of Magic: The Gathering, Pokémon, Yu-Gi-Oh!, and more. From common cards to rare collectibles, we have something for every player and collector.</p>
			<a href="/onlineShop"
			   rel="noopener noreferrer"
			   class="card-action-btn">
				<svg class="card-action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
						  d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6v6L10 14" />
				</svg>
				Visit our online shop
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="feature-card">
			<div class="feature-title-group">
				<div class="feature-icon">🎮</div>
				<h3>Weekly Events</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Join our community for tournaments, draft nights, and casual play sessions. From Friday Night Magic to weekend championships, there's always something exciting happening.</p>
			<a href="/events"
			   rel="noopener noreferrer"
			   class="card-action-btn">
				<svg class="card-action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
						  d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6v6L10 14" />
				</svg>
				View our upcoming events
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="feature-card">
			<div class="feature-title-group">
				<div class="feature-icon">🏆</div>
				<h3>Competitive Play</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Test your skills in our organized tournaments with prizes and rankings. Whether you're a seasoned pro or just starting out, we welcome players of all skill levels.</p>
			<a href="/events"
			   rel="noopener noreferrer"
			   class="card-action-btn">
				<svg class="card-action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
						  d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6v6L10 14" />
				</svg>
				View our upcoming events
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="feature-card">
			<div class="feature-title-group">
				<div class="feature-icon">🎲</div>
				<h3>Table Top</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Explore our selection of board games and tabletop RPGs. From classic strategy games to the latest releases, perfect for game nights with friends and family.</p>
			<a href="/onlineShop"
			   rel="noopener noreferrer"
			   class="card-action-btn">
				<svg class="card-action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
						  d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6v6L10 14" />
				</svg>
				Visit our online shop
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="feature-card">
			<div class="feature-title-group">
				<div class="feature-icon">👥</div>
				<h3>Discord</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Connect with fellow gamers in our welcoming space. Make new friends, join leagues, and become part of Spartanburg's growing gaming community.</p>
			<a href="https://www.discord.com"
			   rel="noopener noreferrer"
			   class="card-action-btn">
				<svg class="card-action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
						  d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6v6L10 14" />
				</svg>
				Join our online community
			</a>
		</div>

		<div class="feature-card">
			<div class="feature-title-group">				
				<div class="feature-icon">✨</div>
				<h3>Expert Staff</h3>
			</div>
			<p>Our knowledgeable team is here to help you build the perfect deck, find that elusive card, or recommend your next favorite game. We're passionate gamers who love to share our expertise.</p>
			<a href="/aboutUs"
			   rel="noopener noreferrer"
			   class="card-action-btn">
				<svg class="card-action-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"
						  d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6v6L10 14" />
				</svg>
				About Us
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

</Layout>